01:17:56,547 --> 01:18:04,597
♪Coming out of the long tunnel on the border,
we find the snow country

926
01:18:05,181 --> 01:18:16,525
♪taking on the stillness of
a bone-chilly night to lay white.

927
01:18:17,318 --> 01:18:39,423
♪～

928
01:18:39,548 --> 01:18:52,645
♪Casting a sidelong glance
at the snowy old townscape,

929
01:18:53,479 --> 01:19:04,740
♪the snow county is just imbued with the memory
of the springtime with you.

930
01:19:06,242 --> 01:19:18,254
♪My hesitation covers the moon
